Package: housepriceindex
Type: Package
Title: A package to construct house price indices from transactions
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alexander Hansen
Maintainer: Alexander Hansen <alexander.g.hansen@hotmail.com>
Description: This package is designed to construct an index of house prices at given targets
    using a list of transactions.
